{"tid":1463799,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你地明未？機場唔係怕示威，係怕黑警的恐襲","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:12.000Z","uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35b540846ebac9dacc8da88582595ebb3ffef94c","tid":1463799,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:50.000Z","msg":"昨日機場停飛，是機場在怕黑警殺入來用臥底搞事再籍機亂射人，之前四次示威都無停機場。所以機場怕的是黑警，不是示威。<br />\n<br />\n現在阻人上機我不認同，不是要割席，而是不同意手法，會上機的人多數都比幾千元買機票，再加請了幾日假期，這對不少人來說是很大的損失。阻人上班已經有點反彈，何況要人損失幾千？<br />\n<br />\n而且你沒發覺黑警反常地不阻止你們的嗎？當你的敵人不去反對你做的事，你是不是要想想為甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n再者，只有幾百人塞的話，黑警最好的策略就是讓你們塞半日，再反常地先客氣地叫你們走，不走就慢慢抬走，反正在機場你們不能在遊客勇武，就只能被抬走。<br />\n<br />\n黑警因此就能得到示威者同遊客對罵和黑警理性克制的鏡頭。"},{"pid":"2094f2ab062878833f789805ce8caea330a7af36","tid":1463799,"uid":9257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:52.000Z","msg":"「破解機場民意論」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"177d3c0e01a09928e1bbbe8e5e3a21b4f09dcbbb","tid":1463799,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74117bb681efb50deb17f0fc877e2cf6afa97b60","tid":1463799,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310df0b977538699c1673cf649f623024767b695","tid":1463799,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1c02ba0308582161787a4128a2782172992ead","tid":1463799,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}